Makefile
--------
use make with optional variables

TYPE={int, double}
switches between types of matrix entries [default: double]

OPT={opt, dbg}
switches between compiling modes [opt: -O3, dbg: -g, default: -O]

TEST={big}
defines name of testset for make check [default: big]

BRANCHING={true, false}
switches between enumeration methods (true: branching tree, false: naive enumeration) [default: true]
NOTE: the naive enumeration is the older and slower version

CUTOFF={true, false}
determines whether subtrees are cut off in the branching tree [default: false]


source files
------------
in bp.c two flags can be defined

DEBUG: prints the solutions
MORE_DEBUG: prints even more information of the solving process
